Package: gl-employee-wifi
Version: 1.0.3
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Employee WiFi Plugin <noreply@example.com>
Section: gl
Priority: optional
Depends: gl-oui-rpc
Description: Employee guest-WiFi page for GL.iNet firmware 4.x.
 Adds a native admin page (set an employee password / no-password / camouflage) and a
 public /wifi page where staff scan and join guest WiFi (hotel, conference, anywhere) as
 the router's uplink, without admin credentials or advanced settings.
 Architecture-independent (Lua + JS + JSON).
